{
  "texts": [
    "Each Tori has its scale and musical tone.",
    "The famous Tori include Gyeong Tori (경토리), Menali Tori (메나리토 리), and Susimga Tori (수심가토리).",
    "For example, the Gyeong Tori mainly comprises the five-note system (sol, la, do, re, mi) and gives a bright and light impression to the audience.",
    "We collect the four types of Tori (Gyeong Tori, Menali Tori, Susimga Tori, Yukjabaeki Tori) with a total of 146 chunks with a 22,050 Hz sampling rate.",
    "The length of each chunk varies from 1 to 10 min."
  ]
}